fields.name: Crew Classic T-Shirt
fields.description:
Our classic crew neck t-shirt in olive. In 100% cotton jersey, peached and gently garment washed for softness. Comfort and style comes hand in hand with this tee.

 100% cotton
 Peached for softness
 Crossed oars embroidered on the chest
 Lead model is 6'0" and wears a size M
 Machine wash at 30 degrees

fields.name: adidas Originals Handball Spezial
fields.description: adidas Originals Handball Spezial Trainers in Aurora Ink, Wild Sepia and Gold Metallic. A firm favourite adopted by fans on the football terraces, as well as the urban warriors and the fashionistas amongst us. Dating back to 1979 when it was first introduced for elite handball players, this beloved shoe is renowned for its classic style. Crafted from soft pigskin nubuck suede for a supple feel and sat atop a contrast gum rubber outsole for a look that simply oozes vintage charm. Regular fitting with a secure lace fastening closure, serrated 3-stripes branding, metallic Spezial Trefoil side motif, and comfortable OrthoLite sock liner.

fields.name: adidas Originals Gazelle Trainer brown / pink / gum
fields.description: adidas Originals Gazelle Trainers in Brown, Pink and Gum. This stallion of a shoe has had an innings of over 70 years and is showing no signs of being bowled out by the competition. Cut into a low profile that showcases a buttery soft leather upper, soft textile lining and durable rubber sole. Regular fitting with a secure lace fastening, classic serrated 3-Stripes to sides, foil Gazelle wording and Trefoil logos to heel tab, tongue and insole.

Body: 100% Cotton. Ribbing: 97% Cotton And 3% Elastane.

fields.name: Roamers Tan Leather & Herringbone Tweed Brogue Boots
fields.description: Combining two of our most favourite fabrics here at MD, tweed and leather, are the Roamers Tan Tween Brogue Boots. They're great for pairing with jeans or chinos and a lightweight dress shirt or t-shirt for a smart casual seasonal look- or even with a pair of cargo joggers if you're feeling a little more adventurous with your styling.

fields.name: Roamers Tan & Navy Suede Chunky Brogues
fields.description:
Its no secret that we love a pair of brogues at Master Debonair. And for good reason. Take these fine examples, for instance.

Theyre the perfect shade of tan and navy to pair with jeans or chinos. We'd even pair them with a tweed suit.

Details such as the contrast stitching punched wingtip toes and classic five-eye lace-up complete these classic brogues. The most comfortable pair of brogues you'll ever wear.

fields.name: Justin Reess Hi Kennedy Brown Tweed Boots
fields.description: Take on any adventure in style with the Justin Reess Hi Kennedy Brown Tweed Boots! These boots are designed for the risk-taker in you, featuring a rugged tweed exterior and sturdy construction. Take bold steps towards your goals and conquer the unknown with these stylish and durable boots!

fields.name: Justin Reess Scott Brown Renaissance Brogues
fields.description: Unleash your daring spirit and elevate your style with the Justin Reess Scott Brown Renaissance Brogues. Featuring a stunning painting print, these brogues offer a unique and bold statement to your wardrobe. Step out of your comfort zone and make a statement with every step.

fields.name: Farah Vintage Revero 3 Pack Boxer Shorts
fields.description: Farah Vintage Revero 3 Pack Boxer Shorts In Dark Grey, Indigo And Stone. Three pairs of cotton stretch boxer shorts in either dark grey, indigo or stone. All three pairs feature a black elasticated waistband with the signature Farah logo repeated round the waistband in yellow and white. 95% Cotton and 5% Elastane.

fields.name: Ralph Lauren Lightweight Oxford Shirt Blue
fields.description: Ralph Lauren Short Sleeve Lightweight Oxford Shirt In Blue, Custom Fit. An all over two toned design and a full front pearlescent button fastening in cream with a pearlescent button down shirt collar and short sleeves. The signature Ralph Lauren Polo Player logo is embroidered on the left of the chest in brown, white, cream and blue. A central pleat on the reverse with a curved hem design and top stitching in blue. 100% Cotton.

fields.name: HUGO BOSS BOSS Regular-Fit Jeans, Bright Blue
fields.description: Explore comfort for fashionable everyday looks with these regular-fit, mid-rise jeans from HUGO BOSS. Made from a cotton blend.

fields.name: Amen Red & Navy Two Tone Brogues
fields.description: Elevate your style game with our Amen Red & Navy Two Tone Brogues. Crafted with precision and sophistication, these shoes exude luxury and elegance. The classic brogue design is given a modern twist with the two-tone color scheme, making them a perfect accessory for any outfit. Walk with confidence and style in these premium brogues.

fields.name: Consort RWR Jacket
fields.description: The Henri-Lloyd iconic Consort RWR Jacket combines heritage style with modern innovation, 100% waterproof, sustainable insulation, and iconic detailing, all crafted from eco-friendly, PFC-free materials for versatile performance.

fields.name: Levi's 512 Slim Tapered Jeans
fields.description:
These all new Levi's 512 jeans offer a tapered twist on the classic 511 slim cut.
 
Crafted from cotton denim with a touch of stretch for comfort, they sit below the waist with a narrow fit through the thigh and a tailor-inspired taper to the ankle.
 
Constructed in a traditional five-pocket silhouette with a zip fly and press stud detailing, their black wash makes them the perfect accompaniment to plain T-shirts and trainers for an edgy look.

fields.name: GANT Regular Gant Jeans
fields.description:
Be the master of relaxed, laid-back dressing with these regular fit jeans from GANT.

Made for off-duty days, consider the cuffs turned up and accenting with lace-up trainers.

Less Laundering
Its best to wash denim as little as possible in order to prevent shrinking and fading. Delay washing your new jeans as long as you can, instead hanging them out on the washing line to air. When they are ready for a freshening up, turn jeans inside-out and wash separately in cold water and line dry, if possible.

fields.description: Nike Air Max 95 Essential Trainers in Black, Dark Grey and Black. Lightweight cushioning with a streamlined aesthetic points towards an unparalleled comfortable ride. Visible Air-Sole unit hugs the full length PU midsole; waffle outsole for traction.

fields.name: Mav Extreme Jacket
fields.description: The Mav Extreme Jacket is the ultimate lightweight shield, offering complete protection and secure storage for tough adventures.

fields.name: Infinite Mav Lite Jacket
fields.description: The Infinite Mav Lite is a lightweight, water-resistant, 100% windproof shell jacket, ideal for dry-weather activities.

fields.name: Viking Smock
fields.description: The Henri-Lloyd Viking Smock is built for adventure, offering unmatched protection with its 3-layer 100% waterproof design and adjustable hood. Made with recycled materials, it's ready for any weather.

fields.name: Lee Carpenter Jeans, Ecru
fields.description: A nod to Lee's workwear heritage, the Carpenter is a comfortable trouser with subtle detailing. Featuring a relaxed fit from the thigh to the knee, with a slight taper at the ankle. Finished off with the authentic hammer loop and extra tool pocket. Carefully constructed with lightweight Oxford canvas including 20% recycled cotton for durability and style. To create a different look, these Carpenters are finished in our off-white Ecru shade. Complete with dark contrast stitching to show off the details.

fields.name: Classic Half Zip Knit Jumper
fields.description:
Our heritage half zip knit in dark navy. Cut from supersoft cotton, this is one of the most versatile pieces in your wardrobe - wear it solo or layer it with a shirt for 9 til 5 style. Effortlessly polished.

 100% cotton
 Ribbed collar, cuffs and hem
 Branded zip pull
 Crossed oars embroidered on the chest
 Machine wash at 30 degrees

fields.name: BOSS 3 Pack Crew Neck T Shirts
fields.description: BOSS 3 Pack Of Classic Crew Neck T Shirts In White, Grey And Navy, Regular Fit. Assorted pack of three regular fit t shirts with ribbed crew necklines and short sleeves. The signature embroidered BOSS logo is situated on the left of the chest on each t shirt in either white or navy. 100% Cotton.

fields.name: Ralph Lauren El Cap Jacket Black
fields.description: Ralph Lauren El Cap Jacket In Polo Black. An all over quilted padded jacket with a full front two way branded zip fastening. Removable and adjustable padded hood with a double press stud fastening throat latch. Half elasticated and velcro fastening cuffs with drawcord fastenings on the interior of the waistband. Three zip entry pockets on the front with the signature Ralph Lauren Polo Player logo embroidered on the left of the chest in red. Shell: 100% Recycled Polyester. Lining: 100% Nylon. Filling: 75% Duck Down And 25% Duck Feathers.

fields.name: Stylus Flare Jeans
fields.description: Add a little retro to your wardrobe to create fashion fun with our Stylus flare jeans. high rise flare leg 5-pockets 32" inseam cotton/polyester/rayon/spandex washable imported

fields.name: BOSS Hooded Tracksuit Navy
fields.description: BOSS Lounge Hooded Tracksuit In Navy. A two piece set with a long sleeved hoodie and joggers. The hoodie has a branded full zip fastening with a large hood featuring a grey interior and grey ribbed cuffs on the long raglan sleeves. Piping detail is featured across the shoulders in grey with a stretch grey ribbed waistband and two pouch pockets on the waist. The signature BOSS logo is embroidered on the left of the chest in grey. The joggers have an elasticated waistband featuring a woven grey drawstring fastening with ribbed ankle cuffs. Two pouch pockets on the hips and the signature BOSS logo is embroidered on the left thigh in grey. Top stitch detail in navy. 95% Cotton And 5% Elastane.

fields.name: St. John's Bay Ikat Sharkbite Tank Top
fields.description: Add our tank top to your warm-weather wardrobe, featuring a sharkbite hem and a flowy style that looks great with shorts or skinny jeans. roundneck sharkbite hem rayon washable imported petite: 30" length misses: 32" length
